{{Quote|I am&mdash;''Sk'ar''! I have the honor to be a general in the Imperial strike force. You&mdash;your city, your pathetic little planet&mdash;have the honor to be my next ''target''.|Bentilais san Sk'ar|<ref name="marvel54">[[Star Wars (1977) 54|''Star Wars'' (1977) 54]]</ref>}}
'''Illyriaqüm''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Calian Confederacy]] on the remote [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Shiva IV]], containing the seat of [[Warlord/Legends|Warlord]] [[Aron Peacebringer]]'s power during the era of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. A large city of gleaming towers, Illyriaqüm was home to the [[Aron Peacebringer's palace|Warlord's palace]] and its richly appointed [[Great Hall (Shiva IV)|Great Hall]].<ref name="marvel53" /> In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[General/Legends|General]] [[Bentilais san Sk'ar]] attempted to destroy Illyriaqüm with an [[anti-matter bomb]] during anniversary celebrations of the [[Concordat of Peace]] between the Calian Confederacy and the [[Twelve Tribes of T'Syriél]], but was foiled by Peacebringer and agents of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].<ref name="marvel54" />

